name: HSBC MSCI USA Climate Paris Aligned UCITS ETF USD (Dist)
description_en: The HSBC MSCI USA Climate Paris Aligned UCITS ETF USD (Dist) seeks to track the MSCI USA Climate Paris Aligned index. The MSCI USA Climate Paris Aligned index tracks US stocks. The parent index is the MSCI USA. The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.12% p.a.. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index by full replication (buying all the index constituents). The dividends in the ETF are distributed to the investors (Semi annually). The HSBC MSCI USA Climate Paris Aligned UCITS ETF USD (Dist) is a very small ETF with 0m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 19 July 2022 and is domiciled in Ireland.
